OL,3,CThird arrest over death of 91-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman in Rotherham
OL,6,FDetectives have made a third arrest in
OL,7,Fconnection with the death of 91-year
OL,8,Fold woman Elizabeth Clark from
OL,9,FRotherham.
OL,11,FA 56-year-old man was arrested on
OL,12,FTuesday 9 June, on suspicion of murder.
OL,14,FElizabeth, who is fondly referred to
OL,15,Fas Betty, was found with serious
OL,16,Finjuries in her home on Peveril Close
OL,17,Fon 11 September 2025.
OL,19,FShe was taken to hospital for
OL,20,Ftreatment but died from her injuries
OL,21,Fjust over two months later.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
