FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781118693
OL,3,CThird arrest over death of 91-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman in Rotherham
OL,6,FOfficers say her bank card was stolen
OL,7,Fthe same day and was used for multiple
OL,8,Ftransactions between 10 and 16
OL,9,FSeptember.
OL,11,FSenior investigating officer,
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Adam Watkinson,
OL,13,Fwho is leading the investigation, said
OL,14,Fthey are conducting several lines of
OL,15,Fenquiry to find out how Betty
OL,16,Fsustained her injuries.
OL,18,F"Betty is missed greatly by those who
OL,19,Fknew her. She was well-loved within
OL,20,Fher community, by many friends and
OL,21,Fneighbours", he said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
