FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781118693
OL,3,CThird arrest over death of 91-year-old
OL,4,Cwoman in Rotherham
OL,6,F"Yesterday's arrest moves us one step
OL,7,Fcloser to finding the answers that
OL,8,FBetty's family deserve."
OL,10,FA 36-year-old man and a 47-year old
OL,11,Fman were previously arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,14,FAll three arrested have been released
OL,15,Fon bail pending further enquiries.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/3
